https://lldcoding.com/design-lld-inventory-management-system-machine-coding

Functional Requirements:
1. User Management
- User should be able to register, login
- User should be able to view and update their profiles
2. Product Management
- Users should be able to add, edit and delete products
3. Inventory Management
- Users should be able to track the quantity of products in stock
- Users should receive alerts when products are back in stock
4. Order Management
- Users should be able to create, view, edit orders
- Users should be able to track the status of the order
5. Payment Management
- Users should be able to choose their mode of payment

Non-Functional Requirements:
